<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Adolf VII., Herzog von Jülich-Berg, Graf von Ravensberg und Herr zu Blankenberg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Peter Fleischmann, Bürger zu Nürnberg, wegen dessen Streit mit Johann von Glevel, Bürger zu Köln und Diener des Adressaten, an und bittet um Unterstützung und Schlichtung.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_10" id="5r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_10_r1l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Adolphen hercʒogen cʒu dem Perge </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l2">Grafen cʒu Rauenſperg vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu <expan>Blankemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_10_r1l3">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> hochwirdıkeit nehſt <expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l4">vnd geantwurtt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / als von <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan> von Glüell ewrs <expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l5">burgers cʒu Colne / vnd des Peter Fleiſchmans <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l6">wegen / vnd als derſelb ~ vnſer Burger <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_line_1573715113818_105">ſache vvegen cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>
<del rend="strikethrough">n</del></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> gnaden </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_10_r1l7"><expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> </ab></add> kümt / vnd die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden cʒu ercʒeln </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l10">maint / Biten vvir ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit allem fleiſʒ / daʒ Jr <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l11"> <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Burger darynne 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>gnedıklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l12">
<del rend="strikethrough">wöllet </del> / vnd Jn <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auſʒrichten wöllet durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l13">Als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> des wol getrawen / Das wöllen vvir v̈mb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l14"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_10" id="5r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Adolphen, herczogen czu dem Perge, grafen czu
                        Ravensperg und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu
                            <expan>Blankemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> hochwirdikeit nehst
                                <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und geantwurtt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> als von <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        von Glüell, ewrs
                                <expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
                        burgers czu Colne, und des Peter Fleischmans,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s,</expan> wegen und als derselb unser burger
                                <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache wegen czu
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<add><expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan></add> kümt und die
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden czu erczeln maint, biten wir ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit allem fleisz, daz ir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burger darynne
                            <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein lassen und in
                                <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auszrichten wöllet durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen, als wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> des wol getrawen. Das wöllen wir ümb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
